# Migrations

`YYYYMMDDHHMMSS_snake_case.sql`, strictly increasing. Every up migration in
`supabase/migrations/` must have a paired rollback in `supabase/rollback/` with
the same timestamp prefix. Apply rollbacks locally via `npm run db:rollback`.
Production rollbacks are a deliberate ops action. Changing an RPC signature:
drop (exact old sig) → create → re-grant.
